    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Because the priests and rulers could not prevail against the clear, calm wisdom of Stephen, they determined to make an example of him; and while thus satisfying their revengeful hatred, they would prevent others, through fear, from adopting his belief. Witnesses were hired to bear false testimony <span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"99\"></span> that they had heard him speak blasphemous words against the temple and the law. &ldquo;We have heard him say,&rdquo; these witnesses declared, &ldquo;that this Jesus of Nazareth shall destroy this place, and shall change the customs which Moses delivered us.&rdquo;",
